en.title: [ENG SUB] Got hit by an earthquake and rockfall while hiking high mountains | Jade Mountain, Taiwan
en.description:
On December 15th, 2022, one day ascending to the highest point of Taiwan, Jade mountain, we got hit by a strong earthquake, followed by a rockfall. This is our video about this trip. 

Huge thanks to everyone who helped us on the way, the hospital staff, and whoever sent us messages of support. Weâ€™re incredibly grateful to you for that!
